### Keymap annotations
#  ::  -->  subsequent command
#  |   -->  alternative command
#  ~   -->  repeatable command
#  ()  -->  order of precedence
#  ,   -->  argument separator
#  ?   -->  optional command / argument
#  #   -->  number argument
#  _   -->  letter argument
#  *   -->  arbitrary argument
#  ~~  -->  to be substituted
#  ""  -->  quotes recommended
#  %+v -->  `cmd + v` to paste

